165
00:10:39.006 --> 00:10:40.907
-And I'll be Barbara.
-It is my house. by the way.

166
00:10:41.842 --> 00:10:43.377
I'm the one paying for it.

167
00:10:44.011 --> 00:10:46.246
-I know.
-(SIGHING): All right.

168
00:10:48.617 --> 00:10:50.382
Okay. so. um...

169
00:10:50.384 --> 00:10:51.451
