196
00:12:01.523 --> 00:12:02.522
You're always at the store.

197
00:12:07.061 --> 00:12:08.428
You want kids. right?

198
00:12:10.264 --> 00:12:11.964
-We both do.
-Well. you know...

199
00:12:11.966 --> 00:12:13.398
