these days.

203
00:12:19.340 --> 00:12:21.740
That's not fair. You know
I had to take time off.

204
00:12:21.742 --> 00:12:23.208
CLARK: Well. it's not my fault
if you can't keep up.

205
00:12:23.210 --> 00:12:24.409
How are you going
to be a lawyer

206
00:12:24.411 --> 00:12:25.612
