211
00:12:35.590 --> 00:12:37.724
I pay for your school. I pay
for your time off school.

212
00:12:37.726 --> 00:12:38.857
I pay for the roof
over your head.

213
00:12:38.859 --> 00:12:40.792
-Can I talk now?
-No! No.

214
00:12:40.794 --> 00:12:42.194
