fat fucking ass and help me!

225
00:13:11.760 --> 00:13:13.460
(EXHALES SOFTLY)

226
00:13:16.096 --> 00:13:17.531
How do you feel. Clark?

227
00:13:23.070 --> 00:13:24.970
